pageProduct.name: Ostelin Vitamin D3 1000IU Liquid - Vitamin D - 50mL
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Maintain muscle & bone strength.

Ostelin Vitamin D3 1000IU Liquid provides an easy to consume daily dose of vitamin D3, the form that is produced naturally in the body.

Vitamin D is a key nutrient which supports general wellbeing as it;

• Maintains bone and muscle strength
• Helps boost calcium absorption
• Supports bone mineralisation
• Maintains healthy immune system function

Vitamin D is made in the skin when exposed to ultraviolet light from the sun. Vitamin D is difficult to obtain from diet alone as not many foods are rich in vitamin D. People who have an indoor lifestyle or who always wear sun protection have been found to be low in vitamin D. Ostelin Vitamin D3 1000IU Liquid maintains vitamin D levels in the body.

Pleasant orange flavour.

Size: 50mL Oral Liquid

KEY FEATURES

• Easy to consume daily dose: Contains vitamin D3 in the form that is produced naturally in the body, and has a pleasant orange flavour
• Vitamin D is a key nutrient that supports general wellbeing: Ostelin Vitamin D3 1000IU Liquid maintains vitamin D levels in the body
• Vitamin D levels: People who have an indoor lifestyle or who always wear sun protection have been found to be low in vitamin D
• Other product benefits: Maintains bone and muscle strength, helps boost calcium absorption, supports bone mineralisation, and maintains healthy immune system function
• Always read the label. Follow the directions for use. Contains orange oil.

Warnings

Always read the label. Follow the directions for use.

Ingredients

Colecalciferol 25 micrograms (1000IU)/0.5mL

Contains: NO ADDED: Gluten, lactose, sugar, artificial colours or flavours, artificial sweeteners or preservatives, or dairy products.

Contains orange oil.

Halal certified.

Directions

For adults and children over 12 years of age: Take 0.5mL daily with a meal or as directed by your healthcare professional.

Enclosed applicator allows for easy, accurate dosing.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C.
Shake well before use.
Refrigerate after opening.
